    INT{"isGenAiIntent()\nisImageGridIntent()\n(intent.ts)"}

    INT -->|Image grid +\nimages selected| LOCAL["createLocalImageGrid()\n— local template, no LLM"]
    INT -->|Gen-AI intent or\nselection has genAiSpec| SEL

