    LLM --> PARSE["parseLLMResponse()\n— extract JSON from markdown\n— validate actions[] + ui{}"]

    PARSE --> MERGE["Merge UISpec\n— replace:true → full replace\n— replace:false → merge controls\n  by ID, preserve stamped\n  defaultValues"]

    MERGE --> DECIDE{actions.length > 0?}

    DECIDE -->|Yes — direct actions| REWRITE
    DECIDE -->|No — has generator| GEN

